{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I told him that he can keep his book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I am not really interested in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Give me half.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He didn't give me anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So I immediately decided that if I ever will be in such a position again, I will tell whoever will send me-- I don't think that I will have another opportunity-- that I found nothing and keep everything to myself.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But I didn't have that much brain at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is just a minor episode.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The important thing is that this hospital grew into significance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we also got stronger in this hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a very influential man, who was a commander, who somehow managed to get weapons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Members of the Hungarian army and even Germans were selling weapons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had some contacts who were buying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had a small, armed group there, which was our resistance, prepared to resist any attack on our lives.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We really had no dreams of attacking the German army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We felt that the second and third Ukrainian army that was attacking the German army was more than adequate to accomplish this task.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at one point, when we were practicing in the basement, our commander came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- we were absolutely frightened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We cannot shoot him because then we are finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he discovered us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he wasn't unfriendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said that he's glad that we have this-- this preparedness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said we should not talk to anybody about this, not even members of our own family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], because before the front comes over us, in his opinion, there will be a commando of fascists to kill this house.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
